  {
    "head": "die Sprache /ˈʃpʁaːxə/",
    "plural": "-n",
    "gloss": ["Language."],
    "notes": [
      "• Feminine noun: die Sprache; after static in, use dative: in der Sprache / in Ihrer Sprache."
    ],
    "examples": [
      {
        "german": "In Ihrer Sprache heißt das anders.",
        "english": "In your language, that is called something different. [formal]"
