  {
    "head": "Ihr- /iːɐ̯/",
    "gloss": ["Your; formal possessive stem."],
    "notes": [
      "• Capitalized Ihr- means formal your. Endings follow ein-words: Ihr Land, Ihre Sprache, in Ihrer Sprache."
    ],
    "examples": [
      {
        "german": "Ihre Sprache ist schön.",
        "english": "Your language is beautiful. [formal; nominative]"
