  {
    "head": "gehen /ˈɡeːən/",
    "gloss": ["To go; walk (+ zu / nach / + place; also set phrases)."],
    "notes": [
      "• Irregular present: ich gehe, du gehst, er geht; for whole countries people often prefer fahren/reisen/fliegen."
